Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，什麼都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚没睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保跟清水老师\N竟然是那种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保你太令人羡慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师不是结婚了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保也不可能是她老公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和有夫之妇…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么是有夫之妇？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜夜春宵的有夫之妇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早不要看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有夫之妇指的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟男人结了婚的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是做早操的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先从手部运动开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么丝茉茉会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我保管，拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人果然很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的，搞什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分钟后要出门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是做这种事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有时会早到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她从来没迟到过的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师到最后还是没来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保那家伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个到底在搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我要这个跟这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过新保那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛又要托我保管丝茉茉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长，手，手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要改变时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为棒球比赛转播
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预定录影的节目\N被延后三十分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要改变设定时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之回背包里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长，那台电脑是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保不知道什么时候\N偷放到我的背包里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说要我帮他保管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来，干嘛要我保管呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既不会成为包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不会妨碍到他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但方便、漂亮\N还什么都会替你做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电脑真的有很多好处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不该对裕美发牢骚的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管牢骚还是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都全年无休，照单全收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是新保那家伙害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请赶快接听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请赶快接听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再响五声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会转到答录机模式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我接通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个声音，你是新保对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟老师私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要插在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是把这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出来，快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有影像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出来，快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，这边才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里…那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，自己接好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师我很高兴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯什么嗯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私奔是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟清水老师现在私奔中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在问你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛跟补习班老师私奔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候\N跟她开始交往的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经快半年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是\N刚到补习班上课的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在我不注意时跟老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我说了也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这么重要的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这台电视不但是旧型  又便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接的方法一定也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没时间烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在必须…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，我去稔家裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要乖乖看家喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么是“私奔”？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是坏事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道\N该怎么回答才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,补习班学生竟然跟老师私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保这个大混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和少爷来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都这么晚了，发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去准备本须和少爷的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真夸张的出场方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托将她接到有画面的电话线上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指超高速通信线路吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想跟谁通电话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞私奔的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,画面会出现在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上会出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，你在国分寺家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续刚刚的话题，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先跟你说也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者应该说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是把你当作朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也当你是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此，为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为多香子不同意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道多香子已经结婚了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次在我那边过夜的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结婚之后马上就迷上电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫妻间的谈话\N变得都是电脑的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子以为他只是\N刚买了电脑高兴过头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以也没在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一段时间之后\N她丈夫就只跟电脑说话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管多香子在不在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只跟电脑？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对电脑不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概想不通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近这种人一直在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得电脑比较可爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和人类比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟电脑在一起比较快乐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些话就是指这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离补习班不远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个小公园对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是刚到补习班的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某天傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我经过那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候还是叫她清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时老师她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在秋千上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为她只是童心大发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想玩玩秋千
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我吃完晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她却还在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为门锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了带钥匙了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙我是有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是上了门链，打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门链是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们吵架了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很久没有吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者应该说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连话都说不上两句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好骂他几句不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她摇了摇头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了门链就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公忘了我会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不在家都没影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得怎样都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得怎样都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明在说这么伤心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她却没有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她其实很想哭出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是拼命在忍耐罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想至少让她在遇到\N不愉快或伤心的事时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够哭个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我迷上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后我就穷追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子认为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是补习班学生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是补习班老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且已经结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我说了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直追，一直追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就变成了今天这个局面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此，为什么要私奔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道只剩这个方法了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们这个年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是小鬼而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许就如同你所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是我的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变得不相信男性的人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她认为就算一开始说喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦出现像电脑那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迎合自己的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会完全改变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像从没喜欢过一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她说过我是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不管说几次她还是不信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次多香子到本须和房间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本打算两人好好谈谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谈谈关于我们的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过事到临头\N她好像还是害怕了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人的心还真是难懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让她跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定私奔到深山的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个好地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样湿答答的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不过是旅行而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩恩爱爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说，这算是私奔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在多香子点头之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:17:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,点头？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚，再婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丝茉茉再帮我保管一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你保管当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟谁在通电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟本须和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比平常性感好几倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜罗，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会再跟你联络的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再有什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告诉我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我这种重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮不了你太大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过或许我可以帮上什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告诉我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，新保这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果只能当个商量的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，还是在室男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是到本须和房间去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我找了一个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我闹得很凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄得他很疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像很困了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几乎是无意识状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我试着问了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经结婚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能喜欢上别人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上一个人，是无法抗拒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对自己的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喜欢上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有对自己都是痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别在其中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己觉得自在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他这么对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然说得出这种大道理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明还是在室男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过不知为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心里像是放下一块大石头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己觉得自在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到他这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了更轻松自在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要到我身边来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没，就是表示快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还叫我新保啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么问题来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜猜\N我一直想要你怎么叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿弘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是个好人，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽是好人却没有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少管我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷上电脑的丈夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算让女孩流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:21:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是觉得电脑比较好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:23:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:23:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:23:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:23:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:23:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.65,0:24:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要更努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更更要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
